    "asOf": "2021-07-22",
    "date": "2021-11-29T17:14:25Z",
    "text": "Adjunct Faculty Loan Fairness Act of 2021\n\nThis bill allows certain part-time faculty to participate in the Public Service Loan Forgiveness (PSLF) program. Specifically, the bill allows part-time faculty members or instructors to participate in the PSLF program if they (1) teach at least one course at an institution of higher education, a postsecondary vocational institution, or a tribal college or university; and (2) do not have another full-time job."
